yanti： yanti（kri）
ယန္တိ（ကြိ）
[yā+a+anti]
[ယာ+အ+အန္တိ]

Yanti，is 3rd pl．pres．of yā： see yāti．-- Note．At D．II，269 we should combine yanti with preceding visamā & sambādhā，thus forming denom．verbs：visamāyanti “become uneven” and sambādhāyanti “become oppressed or tight．” The trsln Dial II．305 gives just the opposite by reading incorrectly．（Page 550）
